							<h6 class="font-semibold text-lg pb-2 pt-1 ">
								Body
							</h6>
							<label class="  pb-2 text-gray-400 text-sm form-group leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">Enter the text for your message in the language
